Class GenDispatchProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.annotation.processing.AbstractProcessor
      • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.processor.GenProcessor
        • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.processor.GenDispatchProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor

    @SupportedSourceVersion(value=RELEASE_6)
@SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.GenDispatch")
public class GenDispatchProcessor
extends GenProcessor
    Processes GenDispatch annotations.

    GenDispatchProcessor should only ever be called by tool infrastructure. See Processor for more details.

    Author:
    Brendan Doherty, Florian Sauter, Stephen Haberman (concept)
